room_title: Escape room "Hangry for History" by Mystery NH in North Conway

room_description:
“Those who don’t study history are doomed to repeat it. Yet those who do study history are doomed to stand by helplessly while everyone else repeats it.”

The Historically Altered Museum, has a new employee. Unfortunately, he also appears to be a sandwich snatcher, which makes me super HANGRY! Find my ham sandwich… PLEASE!
